      <h2 id="project-broadsheet">Project Broadsheet</h2>

      <p>Project Broadsheet is a complete, production-grade static publication system designed for independent journalists, essayists, and editorial teams who want full control over their platform, no subscription fees, no algorithmic gatekeepers, no third-party CMS.</p>

      <p>The full source code is available on GitHub:</p>

